name: "Conjoined Twins on a Unicycle" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Liner pen, crayon, and sticker collage on construction paper with digital embellishments and color.] Here we see the world famous "Holmes Twins" riding a unicycle while being chased by the Black Dog of Death. Go boys! Go! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
